    <title>users/edorgs</title>
    
    <para>
        URI syntax: 
        <filename>https://example.com/api/rest/users/edorgs</filename>
    </para>
    <para>
        Access a list of <varname>stateOrganizationID</varname> values 
        that the current user has permission to access. For SEA 
        Administrators, this includes all education organizations in a 
        tenant. For LEA Administrators, this includes their current 
        education organization.
    </para>
    
